<Defs>

  <ThingDef ParentName="BaseGun">
	<defName>DMS_RapidRPG</defName>
	<label>快反火箭筒</label>
	<description>一次性反装甲火箭推进榴弹发射器，采用简易光学瞄准结构，方便射手快速瞄准，但因此射程有限。结构十分简单，最基础的士兵机兵都可以装备。如果遇到难以对付的重装甲敌人，可以考虑利用巷战和火箭筒送它飞起来！\n\n原版环境是一次性武器，CE环境是可重复装填武器</description>
	<graphicData>
		<texPath>Things/DMS/DMS_RapidRPG</texPath>
		<graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
		<drawSize>1.3</drawSize>
	</graphicData>
	<techLevel>Industrial</techLevel>
	<tickerType>Normal</tickerType>
	<soundInteract>Interact_Rifle</soundInteract>
	<statBases>
		<MaxHitPoints>200</MaxHitPoints>
		<WorkToMake>12000</WorkToMake>
		<Mass>8.8</Mass>
		<MarketValue>1000</MarketValue>
		<RangedWeapon_Cooldown>2</RangedWeapon_Cooldown>
	</statBases>
	<weaponClasses>
      <li>RangedHeavy</li>
    </weaponClasses>
	<weaponTags>
		<li>IndustrialGunAdvanced</li>
		<li>AAC_WeaponOneUse</li>
	</weaponTags>
	<smeltable>true</smeltable>
	<tradeability>Sellable</tradeability>
    <tradeTags>
      <li>WeaponRanged</li>
    </tradeTags>
	<costList>
		<Steel>120</Steel>
		<Chemfuel>30</Chemfuel>
		<ComponentIndustrial>4</ComponentIndustrial>
	</costList>
	<recipeMaker>
      <skillRequirements>
        <Crafting>6</Crafting>
      </skillRequirements>
      <recipeUsers Inherit="False">
        <li>TableMachining</li>
      </recipeUsers>
	</recipeMaker>
	<thingSetMakerTags>
		<li>SingleUseWeapon</li>
		<li>RewardStandardLowFreq</li>
	</thingSetMakerTags>
	<weaponClasses>
      <li>RangedHeavy</li>
	</weaponClasses>
	<relicChance>0</relicChance>
	<verbs>
		<li>
			<verbClass>Verb_ShootOneUse</verbClass>
			<hasStandardCommand>true</hasStandardCommand>
			<defaultProjectile>Bullet_DMS_RapidRPG</defaultProjectile>
			<forcedMissRadius>0.2</forcedMissRadius>
			<ai_AvoidFriendlyFireRadius>5</ai_AvoidFriendlyFireRadius>
			<warmupTime>0.5</warmupTime>
			<range>40</range>
			<soundCast>InfernoCannon_Fire</soundCast>
			<soundCastTail>GunTail_Medium</soundCastTail>
			<!-- 只能手动操作瞄准 -->
			<onlyManualCast>true</onlyManualCast>
			<!-- 可以瞄准地面 -->
			<targetParams>
				<canTargetLocations>true</canTargetLocations>
			</targetParams>
			<muzzleFlashScale>14</muzzleFlashScale>
		</li>
	</verbs>
	<tools>
		<li>
			<label>stock</label>
			<capacities>
				<li>Blunt</li>
			</capacities>
			<power>9</power>
			<cooldownTime>3</cooldownTime>
		</li>
		<li>
			<label>barrel</label>
			<capacities>
				<li>Blunt</li>
				<li>Poke</li>
			</capacities>
			<power>9</power>
			<cooldownTime>1.8</cooldownTime>
		</li>
	</tools>
</ThingDef>

<ThingDef ParentName="BaseBullet">
	<defName>Bullet_DMS_RapidRPG</defName>
	<label>RPG-7</label>
	<thingClass>Projectile_Explosive</thingClass>
	<graphicData>
		<texPath>Things/DMS/RPG7_Shot</texPath>
		<graphicClass>Graphic_Single</graphicClass>
		<drawSize>0.8</drawSize>
	</graphicData>
	<projectile>
		<damageDef>BombSuper</damageDef>
		<damageAmountBase>360</damageAmountBase>
		<explosionRadius>1.9</explosionRadius>
		<arcHeightFactor>1.5</arcHeightFactor>
		<stoppingPower>5</stoppingPower>
		<speed>100</speed>
	</projectile>
</ThingDef>
  
</Defs>